{"tid":2030571,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[國安法］The Campton兩日勁收千五票 超額逾14倍 售樓處續現人龍","createTime":"2020-05-22T23:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T12:26:46.000Z","uid":101341,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"68bd366b597c241522dcc7c396521111bfc710cc","tid":2030571,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:21:09.000Z","msg":"市區新盤混戰，長沙灣新盤The Campton由昨日（21日）開始收票，市場消息指，截至今晚8時，兩日共錄得約1,500認購登記，以首批94伙計算，超額逾14倍。<br />\n<br />\n首張價單94伙，實用面積287至539平方呎，價單定價由576.2萬至1,045萬元，價單呎價17,007元至22,051元，120天即供最高可獲16%折扣，整批單位折實全數平過900萬元，折實售價由484.1萬至877.8萬元，折實呎價14,288元至18,526元。"},{"pid":"2a981f4c703bc7d315c21fcdd6d5071cc26f9182","tid":2030571,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7073e93efaf29f5cbbc7244eba3fcb285fdc8c2","tid":2030571,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:53:05.000Z","msg":"收票又點？<br />\n到真係落注先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2a63c78766fc60774bc449113c6f354939f320","tid":2030571,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9473e16fd5885868ce51015034b7e7d7ac240fd2","tid":2030571,"uid":9633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:19:27.000Z","msg":"龍巿Gogogo"},{"pid":"9f8e18cb9bbb916236e85edd371119a5829e8ac0","tid":2030571,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:28:28.000Z","msg":"都估到必爆, 個盤算唔錯"},{"pid":"9b81e6c0e5b2d420c32f38464e8f73b52aa29467","tid":2030571,"uid":26298,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:37:26.000Z","msg":"一個AA 入幾張飛 <br />\n實爆嫁"},{"pid":"16eab75cd39c5e84e75ca759485b57c8baea30cc","tid":2030571,"uid":83840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":